@node section8 "Version Notes"

                      @{b}Version Notes@{ub}

1.5
---

First public release.

1.52
----

Made a few cosmetic changes to the door.
Accepts longer pathnames.
Users now have single key presses
The document file updated and converted to Amigaguide.

2.0
---

Totally re-written in Amiga E
Accepts pathnames up to 200 chars long! Should be enough!
Some cosmetic changes
Uses reqtools.library by Nico Fracois
Allows multiple selection of files!
Automatically jumps between the maxs and WB screen.

@endnode

@node section5 "Using the door"

                        @{b}Using the door@{ub}

When the door is run you'll be taken to the WB screen and a reqtools file
requestor will open which will allow you to select the files you want to
Raw Download. You can select more than one file to download either by using
the 'All' gadget or by holding down shift and selecting several files.
Pressing 'Ok' will take you back to the Maxs screen where you'll be asked
if you want to proceed with the downloads. After downloading has finished
you'll be asked if you want to send any more files.

@endnode
